plot: Tensions rise in the OCG following the events at Eastfield. With troubling questions hanging over the identity of the mysterious H, suspicions mount among the AC-12 team.

AC-12 discover Corbett's links to Northern Ireland. Arnott arranges, backed up by armed officers. to meet Corbett who tells Arnott that he had beat Hastings's wife Roisin in hospital. Hastings orders Arnott via his wire to shoot Corbett, but he refuses. Corbett reveals the location of a meeting between the OCG and "H" and then escapes. AC-12 and the Cybercrime unit impersonate "H", contacting the OCG via a laptop. The OCG transport a whores cargo to their base to be trafficked. Corbett wants to free them, thinks that McQueen will support him, but OCG retaliate against Corbett realizing he is the rat.—KGF Vissers
